### Changes from PR #28 (by LNLenost)
- Full challenge system with deterministic rotation
- Daily login rewards with streak tracking
- Adventure fixes: join responses, port reuse
- NFC minifig boost support (Mattel tag decoding)
- Token system (claims, redeems, persistent storage)
- Animal tappable fixes (no longer advance hostile mob challenges)
- Completed challenge visibility fixes
- Buildplate instance lifecycle improvements
- Seasons controller
- Updated static data for adventures and shop tabs
